{"tid":1386321,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"救7仔哥哥嘅方法","createTime":"2019-07-30T10:16:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T00:19:18.000Z","uid":259805,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4e2ca0fc338b257ec89760f75fd873cf8dd189a0","tid":1386321,"uid":259805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:16:09.000Z","msg":"我自己都係7仔店員，7仔哥哥係照足程序去做，又勇又鎮定！<br />\n如果咁都比人炒，無理由唔幫佢或者玩殘7仔！！<br />\n<br />\n方法就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">投訴</span></span>！投訴涉及嗰間店（信德中心地下)甚至各區嘅店鋪！<br />\n唔一定要真係搵人投訴，可以投訴啲無聊野<br />\n<br />\neg貨品無跟日期先出先入(即係限期後啲嘅貨反而放最前)、飲品唔夠凍、貨品缺貨<br />\n甚至投訴佢亂咁炒人<br />\n<br />\n牛奶公司處理投訴要有好多程序，要負責投訴部門通知各區主任，再由主任同店鋪去睇cctv，之後交翻報告比高層，又要再set課程資料。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X5THSkp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX5THSkp.png&h=55941d2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">支持7仔哥哥，支持良心店鋪，不忘五大訴求！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">8月5三罷 一齊努力</span>"},{"pid":"b37e40285e1be02b90e2306e81c8d2bcdf4b1a8a","tid":1386321,"uid":81631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:20:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"efe9a4247ab5e240694fbfed080775f4ac790e77","tid":1386321,"uid":250594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:20:23.000Z","msg":"而家有話佢比人炒？定係開定先"},{"pid":"a6c0024ddc7904f928e46b917a755840151e9202","tid":1386321,"uid":259805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efe9a4247ab5e240694fbfed080775f4ac790e77","tid":1386321,"uid":250594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:20:23.000Z","msg":"而家有話佢比人炒？定係開定先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:22:08.000Z","msg":"有人話收到風，出定po預防萬一😞😞😞<br />\n7仔哥哥咁勇擋住"},{"pid":"853ea318ae7364068545f0f5d06d46efd2c9c636","tid":1386321,"uid":2660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:35:29.000Z","msg":"7仔唔會亂炒人 <br />\n最多調佢去其他舖過冷河<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma